Package me.gamercoder215.superadvancements.advancement.criteria.trigger

Enum Class DamageTag

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<DamageTag>
me.gamercoder215.superadvancements.advancement.criteria.trigger.DamageTag
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<DamageTag>, Constable, Keyed
public enum DamageTag extends Enum<DamageTag> implements Keyed

Represents a Damage Tag for the Damage Criteria Trigger.

This only exists in 1.19.4+ and above. To ensure the API evolves correctly, this is generally not supported on versions below that.
